    "The <b>Lead Bow</b> is a low tier <linked>bow</linked> crafted using <linked>Lead Bars</linked>. It is stronger than the lowest tier of <linked>ore</linked> bows, the <linked>Copper Bow</linked> and <linked>Tin Bow</linked>, and is even slightly stronger than its counterpart, the <linked>Iron Bow</linked>. Like the other bows, its sole purpose is to fire <linked>arrows</linked> from a distance to damage enemies.",
